### YouTube Content Pipeline — Sample API Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client, JetBrains HTTP Client, or httpx

@base_url = http://localhost:8080

# ── Health & Info ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{base_url}}/health

### API info
GET {{base_url}}/

# ── Full Pipeline ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Run full pipeline: tech niche for next Tuesday
POST {{base_url}}/pipeline
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request": "Create a YouTube Short about the latest AI breakthroughs in healthcare",
  "niche": "tech",
  "creator_id": "default",
  "deadline": "Tuesday"
}

###

### Run full pipeline: finance niche, no deadline
POST {{base_url}}/pipeline
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request": "Make a Short about why the stock market is dropping this week",
  "niche": "finance",
  "creator_id": "default"
}

###

### Run full pipeline: fitness niche
POST {{base_url}}/pipeline
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "request": "Create a viral fitness Short about intermittent fasting myths",
  "niche": "fitness",
  "creator_id": "default",
  "deadline": "Saturday"
}

# ── Chat Interface ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Ask coordinator for topic ideas only
POST {{base_url}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are the top 5 trending tech topics I should cover this week? Just give me ideas, don't start producing anything.",
  "user_id": "creator_1"
}

###

### Research a specific topic
POST {{base_url}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Research the topic 'OpenAI o3 model release' for me. I need key facts and statistics for a YouTube Short.",
  "user_id": "creator_1"
}

###

### Script only (no production)
POST {{base_url}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Write me a YouTube Short script about Elon Musk's Grok 3 AI. Use a tech niche style. Don't produce the video, just the script.",
  "user_id": "creator_1"
}

###

### Continue conversation (use session_id from previous response)
POST {{base_url}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Can you make that script more aggressive and punchy? Less than 150 words.",
  "user_id": "creator_1",
  "session_id": "REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID_FROM_PREVIOUS_RESPONSE"
}

###

### Run analytics
POST {{base_url}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Run analytics for video ID 'dQw4w9WgXcQ' in the tech niche. Give me a performance report.",
  "user_id": "creator_1"
}

# ── Job Status ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Check pipeline job status (replace with real job_id)
GET {{base_url}}/pipeline/REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID

###

### Trigger analytics for a job (48h post-publish)
POST {{base_url}}/pipeline/REPLACE_WITH_JOB_ID/analytics?youtube_video_id=dQw4w9WgXcQ&niche=tech
